Hotel Management System – Java Full Stack
A modular hotel management system built with Java and Object-Oriented Programming (OOP) principles. The system simulates real hotel operations, including client check-in/out, room availability, and reservation management. This project demonstrates practical application of Java, structured business logic, and modular system design.

Key Skills: Java, OOP, Data Structures, Exception Handling, MVC Architecture (planned)



Phase 1 – Planning & Structure

Definir requisitos (CRUD, reservas, GUI, relatórios)
